10: The cave Shpella e Blazit, the entrance—green arrow. 11: Shpella e Blazit, on the entrance. 12: Shpella e Blazit, topographical sketch. 13: Distribution of the genus 
<emphasis box="[770,1131,1869,1893]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="591">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1910" box="[770,899,1869,1893]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Bathyscidius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="591" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Bathyscidius</taxonomicName>
— 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1910" box="[925,1054,1869,1893]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Bathyscidius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="591" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Bathyscidius</taxonomicName>
(s.str.),
</emphasis>
four species from Croatia (1- 4), one species from Montenegro (5); 
<emphasis box="[543,877,1905,1929]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="591">
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="Polak &amp; Jalzic" authorityYear="2019" box="[543,872,1905,1929]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Bathyscidius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="591" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ionobathyscidius">Bathyscidius (Ionobathyscidius)</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
one species from Albania (7), one species from North Macedonia (6), 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,617,1941,1966]" pageId="3" pageNumber="591">
<taxonomicName authority="Čeplík &amp; Lakota &amp; Čeplík, 2021" authorityName="Čeplík &amp; Lakota &amp; Čeplík" authorityYear="2021" box="[312,529,1941,1965]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Bathyscidius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="591" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basarai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,529,1941,1965]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="591">Bathyscidius basarai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[536,617,1942,1966]" pageId="3" pageNumber="591" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
from Albania (8).
</paragraph>
